description:
Proper Japanese Title: ジャンプSQ.CROWN

Spin-off magazine of regular Jump SQ, Crown is a seasonal publication, released once a quarter. Though it is home to a few ongoing serials that were moved there from other magazines (most significantly, D.Gray-man which had previously been known for regular hiatuses), like most Jump SQ spin-offs, at its core it is meant to publish one-shots from an assortment of creators.

Titles serialized in this magazine include:

  • Bōken ō Bīto
  • D.Gray-man
  • Kekkai Sensen: Back 2 Back
name: Jump SQ.CROWN
